---
title: Parsley Butter Pork Tenderloin with Dauphinoise Potatoes & Baby Rainbow Carrots
description: Bring some French-inspired flair to your table with this sublime dish! Starting with a premium pork fillet and some creamy
dauphinoise potatoes, then finishing with roasted baby carrots and crisp sautéed asparagus, you're in for a treat!

